-- Ana Ivanovic Begins Day 4 at U.S. Open With Second-Round Victory
-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 2012-08-30T16:24:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-30/ana-ivanovic-begins-day-4-at-u-s-open-with-second-round-victory.html
Ana Ivanovic advanced to the third
round of the U.S. Open with a 6-2, 6-2 victory over Sofia
Arvidsson of  Sweden .  Ivanovic, the women’s 12th seed from Serbia, opened the
day’s play on the main Arthur Ashe Stadium court at the National
Tennis Center in New York.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
